      | BEATTY-DICKENS                |
      | VANDERVORT, CRONA AND TRANTOW |
      | NIKOLAUS AND SONS             |
      | PAGAC INC                     |
      | JOHNS, GLEASON AND WHITE      |
      | PFANNERSTILL-KUTCH            |
      | MOSCISKI-ROHAN                |

    Examples:
      | dayly_rate  |
      | -8.7        |
      | Lanz        |

